'''''Kaddu Beykat''''' ( Letter from My Village cyagwa ''Lettre paysanne'' ) ni filime yo [[Senegali|muri Senegal yo mu]] 1975 iyobowe na Safi Faye<ref>https://www.cccb.org/en/activities/file/kaddu-beykat/235140</ref> . Niyo filime ya mbere yerekanwe yakozwe n’umugore wo muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara yatanzwe mu bucuruzi kandi izana amahanga ku muyobozi wayo. <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/letter-from-my-village-kaddu-beykat/</ref> <ref>https://africa.film/kaddu-beykat-a-safi-faye-feature-film/</ref> Ishingiye ku rukundo, ivuga ubuzima bwa buri munsi bw'abantu bo mucyaro cya Senegal<ref>http://lightindustry.org/safifaye</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Ngor ni umusore uba mu mudugudu wa Senegali wifuza kurongora Coumba. amapfa yo mu mudugudu afite ingaruka kubihingwa<ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.film.letter-from-my-village-kaddu-beykat.7293.html</ref>, nuko Ngor ntashobore kubona  inkwano ya Columba<ref>https://www.torinofilmfest.org/en/16-torino-film-festival/film/kaddu-beykat/1276/</ref>. Yagiye mu murwa mukuru wa Senegali, Dakar, kugira ngo agerageze gushaka amafaranga menshi<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/au/film268466.html</ref> . Agaruka ku baturage maze abwira abandi ibyamubayeho mu mujyi<ref>http://www.filme-aus-afrika.de/EN/film-database/a-z/film-details/w/10839/</ref>. Iyi nkuru yerekana ubuzima bwa buri munsi bw'abaturage, ivuga uburyo bw'ibaruwa yandikiye inshuti ye, izwi nka Faye. <ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/kaddu-beykat/cast/2000025481/</ref>

